column2: "〔I will say〕〔Still〕〔Do not acknowledge you〕〔Get along〕〔No intention〕"
"〔But〕〔Must repay debt〕〔That is〕〔Out of pride〕〔Do not misunderstand〕"
"It's him! That masked guy from the tundra."
"He sure has a knack for showing up at the worst times!"
"It looks like he's not about to let you go, <%me>."
